text: David John Trone (born September 21, 1955) is an American Democratic politician and businessman. He was a member of the United States House of Representatives from Maryland's 6th congressional district from 2019 to 2025. He co-founded and co-owns Total Wine & More. He was an unsuccessful candidate for the U.S. Senate in 2024. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Maryland Category:Businesspeople from Maryland Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
